on Raceway|DAR]]<br><small>20</small>\n|colspan=2|\n!style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| 5th\n!style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| 1.027,5\n|-\n! rowspan=1| [[1951 AAA Championship Car season|1951]]\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1951 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]<br><small>9</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Langhorne Speedway|LAN]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Darlington Raceway|DAR]]<br><small>2</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Illinois State Fairgrounds Racetrack|SPR]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]<br><small>10</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[DuQuoin State Fairgrounds Racetrack|DUQ]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[DuQuoin State Fairgrounds Racetrack|DUQ]]<br><small>1</small>\n| [[Pikes Peak International Hill Climb|PIK]]\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Great New York State Fair|SYR]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Michigan State Fairgrounds Speedway|DET]]<br><small>4</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Littleton, Colorado|DNC]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[San Jose, California|SJS]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Desert Diamond West Valley Phoenix Grand Prix|PHX]]<br><small>13</small>\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Bay Meadows Racetrack|BAY]]<br><small>2</small>\n!style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| 1st\n!style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| 2.556\n|-\n! rowspan=1| [[1952 AAA Championship Car season|1952]]\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1952 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]<br><small>24</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFCFCF;\"| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]<br><small>DNQ</small>\n| [[Raleigh Speedway|RAL]]\n| [[Illinois State Fairgrounds Racetrack|SPR]]\n| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]\n| [[Michigan State Fairgrounds Speedway|DET]]\n| [[DuQuoin State Fairgrounds Racetrack|DUQ]]\n| [[Pikes Peak International Hill Climb|PIK]]