2</small>\n|colspan=2|\n!style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| 1st\n!style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| 1.830\n|-\n! rowspan=1| [[1959 USAC Championship Car season|1959]]\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;| [[Daytona International Speedway|DAY]]<br><small>18</small>\n|style=\"background:#ffffbf;| [[Trenton Speedway|TRE]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#dfffdf;| [[1959 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]<br><small>4</small>\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]<br><small>17</small>\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;| [[Langhorne Speedway|LAN]]<br><small>17</small>\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;| [[Illinois State Fairgrounds Racetrack|SPR]]<br><small>17</small>\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]<br><small>16</small>\n|style=\"background:#ffdf9f;| [[DuQuoin State Fairgrounds Racetrack|DUQ]]<br><small>3</small>\n|style=\"background:#cfeaff;| [[Great New York State Fair|SYR]]<br><small>6</small>\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;| [[Indiana State Fair|ISF]]<br><small>15</small>\n|style=\"background:#dfdfdf;| [[Trenton Speedway|TRE]]<br><small>2</small>\n|style=\"background:#ffffbf;| [[California State Fairgrounds Race Track|SAC]]<br><small>1</small>\n|style=\"background:#efcfff;| [[XM Satellite Radio Indy 200|PHX]]<br><small>8</small>\n|colspan=2|\n!style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| 2nd\n!style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| 1.430\n|-\n! [[1960 USAC Championship Car season|1960]]\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Trenton Speedway|TRE]]<br><small>2</small>\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1960 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]<br><small>23</small>\n|style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]<br><small>4</small>\n|style=\"background:#FFCFCF;\"| [[Langhorne Speedway|LAN]]<br><small>DNQ</small>\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Illinois State Fairgrounds Racetrack|SPR]]<br><small>15</small>\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Milwaukee 225|MIL]]<br><small>14</small>\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[DuQuoin State Fairgrounds Racetrack|DUQ]]<br><small>2</small>\n|style=\"backg